        >
          <h2 style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700">
            Ares Acquires GCP’s Non-China Assets in Big Deal
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          padding="10px 12px"
          font-family="EB Garamond"
          color="#000000"
        >
          <p
            style="
              font-size: 18px;
              line-height: 1.6;
            "
          >Ares Management is making a <a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/why-lockheed-lmt-could-beat-161015756.html" target="_blank">bold move</a> by acquiring GLP Capital Partners’ assets outside China for $5.2 billion. The deal boosts Ares' real estate portfolio, nearly doubling its assets under management to $96 billion. Ares will pay $1.8 billion in cash and $1.9 billion in shares, with an additional $1.5 billion possible if performance targets are hit. This acquisition strengthens Ares’ global presence in logistics, digital infrastructure, and renewable energy sectors.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider
          border-width="1px"
          border-style="solid"
          border-color="lightgrey"
          padding="10px 12px"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
